⍝ DropAxis.tc
⍝ ═══════════

      ⎕IO←1

      ⍝ Precond: A integer; X∊⍳⍴⍴B
      ⍝ inv: (⍴Z)[,X] ←→ 0⌈(⍴B)[,X]-|A
      ⍝ inv: ⍴⍴Z ←→ ⍴⍴B
      ⍝ inv: A↓B ←→ A↓[⍳⍴⍴B]B
      B ← ⎕RVAL 2 (5 6) (,0 1 0 0 0)
      A ← 2∣⎕RVAL 0                          ⍝ drop 0 or 1 along axis 1
      Z ← A↓[1]B
      ((⍴Z)[1]) ≡ 0⌈(⍴B)[1]-|A
1
      (⍴⍴Z) ≡ ⍴⍴B
1
      ⍝ inv: A↓B ←→ A↓[⍳⍴⍴B]B for vectors
      B ← ⎕RVAL 1 (,6) (,0 1 0 0 0)
      A ← 2∣⎕RVAL 0
      (A↓B) ≡ A↓[⍳⍴⍴B]B
1
